What is the projected market size & growth rate of the Sports Protective Equipment Market?

Market Analysis and Insights

Sports protective equipment market size is valued at USD 9.66 billion by 2028 and is expected to grow at a compound annual growth rate of 5.42% for the forecast period of 2021 to 2028. Sports protective equipment market report analyses the growth, which is currently being growing due to the increase in demand for the sporting goods and rising popularity of sports leagues.

Sports protective equipment is the type of tools that protect one while playing games and sports. It is specially designed in such how that it brings ease while playing a sport and safety from any accident which can occur while playing.

The rapidly escalating levels of spending on sports equipment devices by consumers is one of the primary factors driving the sports protective equipment market growth rate. Moreover, the substantial increase of international and national sports events as well as the high growth in consumer awareness regarding health and fitness is also fueling the growth of the sports protective equipment market in the forecast period of 2021 to 2028.

Also the market is largely driven by the rapid increase in consumer spending on sports equipment. Additionally, the growing interest in personal appearance amongst the individuals, promoting health consciousness among people, increasing population and rising disposable incomes are also highly impacting the growth of the sports protective equipment market. While, the increase in participation in sports activities and surge in participation is endorsed to ever-increasing campaigns by sports governing bodies and professional leagues which are also one of the major factors driving the growth of the sports protective equipment market in the above mentioned forecast period. In addition, the significant growth in consumer awareness regarding the health benefits presented by indulging in physical activities along with rapid technological advancement in sports protective equipment and development of advanced protective equipments will further bring various opportunities that will lead to the growth of the sports protective equipment market in the above mentioned forecast period.

However, the increasing threat of counterfeit products and high pricing of good quality sports equipment are the major limiting factor for sports protective equipment market, whereas the, lack of awareness regarding the product have the potential to challenge the growth of the sports protective equipment market in the forecast period of 2021 to 2028.

